ENTRY
- date
- start
- stop
- color
- description
- hashtags
  - colors determine default tags
  - case-insensitive

RECORD
- SPACE start rec
  - C color
  - D description
- SPACE stop rec
- E manually enter END of current interval (use case: forgot to end it)
- R RESUME last thing
- M MANUAL entry

ANALYZE
- ...a day
- sum up each tag (or color)
  - sorted by what you spent most of your time on
  - show mins/h:mm/percent
- merge tags

V2
- half-and-half
- batch edit
- record: start a new one and finish the last one

V3
- analyze: split tags
